Dialogue: 3,0:22:18.73,0:22:23.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}都会化作气泡消失掉
Dialogue: 3,0:22:23.57,0:22:25.66,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}哭泣忧愁又烦恼
Dialogue: 3,0:22:25.86,0:22:27.87,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}无数往事多纷扰
Dialogue: 3,0:22:28.16,0:22:31.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}都没关系的
Dialogue: 3,0:22:32.25,0:22:34.75,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}所有往事尽怀抱
